    	<p><strong>Writing your Personal Statement:</strong></p>


<p>In this video you’ll hear from a fourth year medical student and a sixth form tutor who discuss how to make the most of your personal statement.

<p>The important thing is that the statement is obviously yours and captures your character and personality. <p>However, there are key things you’ll need to include.  <p>This video will describe them and suggest one way of structuring your information.



		
    	
  		
